-1 STORY~
It is a time of turmoil.  The Mist rolls in from the dark, bringing with it
evil and death.  Life as it once was, is no more. A great power claws at the
landscape, perverting it, shaping it into its own image.  The darkness grows 
more powerful by the day, is there hope for the light?
~

