                      Galliard      Ahroun
~

0 Ragabash~
- Blur - Syntax: Blur - This makes you appear invisible to anyone in the 
  room. Except to those with heightened senses.
- automatic - It makes your feet leave no tracks.
- Tail - Syntax: tail (person) - This is the wolves primary attack power.
- Readaura - Readaura (person/item) - This allows you to see the stats on a 
  person or item.
- automatic - This gives you an immunity to silver.
~

0 Theurge~
- Mother - Syntax: Mother (person) - This restores some of their hps.
  And any wounds that need to be mended.
- Scent - Syntax: Scent - This allows you to see into the shadow world. The 
  Umbra
- Spiritguardian - Syntax: Spiritguardian - This summons a guardian from the 
  spirit world to alert you if people are trying to do things to you.
~

0 Philodox~
- automatic - You can resist pain more easily
- Scry - Syntax: Scry (target) - this allows you to see through your victims 
  eyes.
- Wallgranite/Wallwater - Syntax: wallg (direction) OR wallw (direction) - 
  This makes a wall that doesn't allow people to flee
~

0 Galliard~
- Wyld - Syntax: Wyld - This calls out to any Werewolves to come to your aid 
  during a battle.
- Beastwithin - Syntax: Beast - This makes you rage right away (willpower 
  animalism MUST be down)
~

0 Ahroun~
- Truefear - Syntax: Truefear (target) - The power makes the enemy flee in 
  terror.
- Hand - Syntax: Hand - This makes your hands light up in flames
~


0 TRIBE TRIBES TRIBEGIFT TRIBEGIFTS~

Each tribe has its own talents and special powers.  Tribe Gifts are passed
down through generations.  Most tribal Gifts originate with that tribe's
totem spirit or an allied spirit.

	       +-+-+-+-+-+-+   +-+-+   +-+-+-+   +-+-+-+-+-+
