           Get of Fenris      Red Talons             Shadow Lords

           Silent Striders    Silver Fangs           Stargazers

           Uktena             Wendigos               Bone Gnawers
           Glass Walkers

For information on each tribe's Gifts, type help <tribe>.
~


0 TEACHGIFT~
Syntax: teachgift <character> <gift>
 
This command enables the Werewolf to teach his learned gifts to another
Werewolf. Of course, only the knowledge which has been consolidated can
be taught, which means in practical terms that only gifts at level 3
or higher can the taught.
 
See also: TRIBEGIFT
~
0 'Black Furies'~
