0 PUNISHMENT~
These are the punishments you will recieve for breaking rules.
*Multiplaying:
First Offence - Deletion of lesser charactor.
Second Offence - Deletion of greater character.
Third Offence - Deletion of all charactors.
*Wrongful use of Charm Spell:
First Offence - Frozen in MS for Free Decapitation.
*Leaving a Character Morted for 5 minutes or more: 
First Offence - Frozen
Second Offence - Frozen in MS for Free Decapitation.

Others:
First offense:   A warning.   (depends on severity of the rule broken)
Second offense:  Silenced for a minimum of 3 minutes.
Third offense:   Crib for at least 10 minutes.
Fourth offense:  A good chance you'll lose status.  *grin*
Fifth offense:   A deny for a minimum of 1 day. (up to the imm setting it)
Sixth offense:   Pray you don't get here.
 * deny == banning of that character

Depending on the "repeat offense" factor..   some players MAY
not have the liberty of getting warned or cribbed.

Disrespect of any immortals, including but not limited to complaining off the
mud of mud-related issues, harassment etc. etc. is consider a no-tolerance issue.
~

0 HQ HEADQUARTERS~
Clans will have the option to purchase their own headquarters. 
  
  *HQ's will start with three basic rooms: a recall room, a safe room, and a porter room.  
    COST: 2500 quest points, additional rooms will cost 1000 quest points each.
    HQ's will be designed by the clan leader, who can include low level mobs, objects, 
    and a healer.

  *The transporter room will come with 5 pre-picked destinations, additional may be
   purchased for 500 quest points per location, max of 15 porters total. (no porters to
   other HQ's will  be allowed)
  
  *Clan guardians may also be purchased.
     Basic guardians cost 2000 quest points, and are about the level of an Atlantis 
     Guard (level 800).
       Guardians can be upgraded for 1000 quest points per 100 levels (max 1500).
       Once your first guardian has reached level 1500, another guardian may 
       be purchased. (Max 3)

Please see HQFORMAT
~

0 Hqf Hqformat~
It would be appreciated if hqs were sent to Mystaria@cheerful.com in the following
format.

ROOM NAME
Room exits (e,w,n,etc and what room they connect to, and no, you can't add you own color)
Room Description (Please keep length to a paragraph or two.)
Room flags (porter room, safe, dark, indoors, etc)
Extra description (porter sign, etc, not object)

OBJECT IN ROOM (name)
short
long
look (optional)
object type and wear location (furniture, armor-neck, etc, else will be made trash)
object flags (ac, hp, etc, not half as strong as class eq)

MOB IN ROOM (name)
short
long
look (optional)
mob level and sex (or will be level 1, neutral sex, except healer which is lev 500)
mob flags (healer, guardian, sentinal, infravision, sanc, etc)
Eq on mob (same format as OBJECT)

NEXT ROOM NAME... and so on.

Also, please spell check and grammar check them.
This will help your hq be built quicker, and will ensure that it is built correctly.
Hqs not in this format will be made at my whim... no complaints.
~

