0 KREL~
Ages have passed since the creation of the world and the dawn of time. 
Since then there have been those who would choose to walk the path of the 
adversary. These damned souls have taken up residence in the halls of 
hell and seek to destroy everything and everyone, even each other. Those who 
took the road only serve themselves. They wish no change in the world that 
does not benefit them directly. Almost as weak in soul as the demons of 
spite these creatures want only chaos. Those who follow the path of 
enlightenment have come closer to the Above. These pure souls have realized the 
consciousness of mortals and the will of demons only affects the will 
of those who would be controlled.

We of the enlightened path strive to create a cleaner whole by purging 
the world of the Wyrm's children. The children of Gaia and the spiteful 
Ninja clans are of little concern to us. Those who would undermine the will 
of the Above and those who follow the ways of the Wyrm are to be stamped out 
like a poorly built fire.


OOC:

First of all I would like to say that I have quite a reasonable amount 
of skill with this class and am more that willing to teach the finer 
points to those who choose to follow me. On the other hand I am going to require 
that you work a great deal for your angelhood, I'm not one to dole out 
every piddling power just because you meet my stat Reqs.

That being said I would also like to say that if you do work for your  
powers and armor you'll find me that much more behind you. I smile upon  
those who help themselves.

I am also rather big on RP. Those who want to get into bed with the  
demons or the vampires can do so, but not under my tag. I also don't fancy 
those who use bugs or glitches unfairly.

That having been said I my requirements are as follows:
  - 6k/4k/5k Hp/Mana/Mv
  - Tiger or Dragon to GM
  - Unarmed and one other weapon GMed
  - 100 blue

I would also appreciate being notified as to your intents if you plan 
to try for classing angel. I will most certainly answer any question and    
check you from time to time. I will more than likely have a test of 
some sort the check you and will follow your growth as a player. A large 
part of acceptance is the impression I get from you as a person and a player.  
'Hey d00d could U class me?'- is not something I'm going to like.

Thank you.
    Krel Sargidev
~
0 VENTRUE SIVAR~
**Please Note Ventrue is closed to classing**

I will be blunt, if you are looking for an
easy clan to join, Ventrue is not for
you.  Only the best will be chosen to be given the gift of eternal life, and join the
ranks of the clan.

A few things we are looking for in a childe:
* Dedication to the clan.
* Initiative.
* A vast knowledge of vampire abilities, strengths and weaknesses.
* Knowledge of how to use vampire strengths, and how to protect your weakness.
* Knowledge of other race's weakness, and how to exploit them.
* Ruthlessness.

Of less importance, yet still a vital factor, are the statistical requirements:
* 4K across.
* All stances up to and including Dragon GM'd.
* Slash, Bite, Unarmed, and Pierce GM'd.
If you impress me these can be over looked, and will not be held against you for
clanning.  However, and this goes for all clan members, once you become a Ventrue, you
are expected to grow as fast as possible.

For those that choose to take the path to becoming a Ventrue know this, you are joining
an elite group.  We were the first to be embraced by our lord and god Xentoth.  Therefore
we have the duty to uphold the status of all vampires, and to lead the younger clans, by
example, to glory.  All Ventrue stand together, we are a family, linked together through
blood.  One members problem becomes the clans problem, and is delt with as I see fit.  We
protect our allies, and drink the souls of our enemys.  Together we will rain terror and
death apon the living.  I expect all that join the clan to strive for this goal.  An in the
end we will retire to our headquarters to sit atop our thrones carved of bone, amongst the
decaying corpses of our enemies, and enjoy a warm chalice of blood.

Sivar <Founder of #0Ventrue#n>
(Please note, Ventrue is closed.)
~

