0 RED TALONS CARVVO~
#R**#0A man stands in the middle of the twon square as you walk by. THis man is surounded by people throwing rocks and sticks at him...calling him ugly...and kicking him to the ground. You can see the man is a bit disfigured in the face and has many scars. You can tell the man is getting angry as his face is stuck in a permanent grimace. The man stands up in the middle of the crowd and SCREAMS!!! They all hold their heads in aggony. As they stand their stunned, he starts howling and his body begins to grow into an enormous beast. He appears to be half man and half wolf. He screams in rage as he rips the limbs off of the people in the crowd. One man tries to run but has his head ripped off by the beast. The beast stands over the dead bodies then walks to a post and nails a letter to it. He howls when he is done and runs off into the woods leaving nothing but death and destruction behind him. As you walk up to the letter you see it's written in blood. You read the note as follows.#R** 

#R**#0 To join the ranks of the Red Talons you must have 5k across and have GMed 1 stance and 1 weapon. 

For Elder you must be 15k HP and have all stances GMed and 3 wepaons GMed.#R** 

#R**#0You feel yourself clenching you fists as you read the note. You feel yourself wanting to be as powerful as the beast you just saw. You run off into the woods to find the strange man. You're going to join the Red Talons and rip some people apart.#R** 

