0 RAVNOS ISHAMAEL~
If ever a clan  was renowned for a wickedly black sense of humor, the Ravnos 
would be that clan. These Cainites are decievers of the first order, weaving 
illusion and lies into elabourate schemes to part the foolish from whatever 
it is the Ravnos might fancy - Be it wealth, blood, or even the victims 
freedom.    So, you wish to join the illustrious ranks of the wandering 
bandits, cutthroats, swindlers, and sneak-thieves?  Well, you've come to the 
right place.
The Ravnos are a tight knit familia, bound to their strict code of 'honor', 
which may or may not coincide with another cainites code, and will defend t 
heir 'good name' until the end..depending on what they view as slander.    
And as such they will come to the aid of their  clannmates, and vice versa. 
We may take advantage of each other, but it's our priviledge. Others are not 
allowed to do the same.  Our business in the Jhyhad is just that .. our 
business.    Eagerly do we wallow in our vices, tis the only way to live, to 
unlive, is to enjoy it.   Now then, you've listened to enough of this old 
man's rambling. On to business. What you will have when you come to me, 
seeking entry.

Entry unto the familia -

7,000 hp, mana, move
Swallow or Dragon Stance
Unarmed, and Bite trained (Use British Sceptre and Sting, they work 
marvelously)
At least 50 blue

You WILL be Sired by myself, or my Princess, whom will be the Only Princess. 
  Also, you will be conditioned by myself, for security reasons. Failure to 
submit is to be cast into the ranks of the Pariah.

Prince Status -

I will have one Princess - Irina. You are not her so this is not yours.


Thus I sign my hand,


Ishamael Bgreathiou
Prince of Midgaard
Antediluvian of the Second Generation.
~
