0 STORMCALLERS DAKEYRAS~
As the Stormcallers are a mercenary clan, you will be mercenary. 
Any contracts for assistance or slaughter will be accepted, so long as they do not violate the basic principle of "Avenge all wrongs." 

To this end, honour is simple: 
Anything worth killing is best killed alone, but if it's too ugly, getting help is always a refreshing change. Mind you, that's only of interest to the beginners. Anyone truly good can butcher most anything alone. As it should be. 

If it hurts you, hurt it back. Much worse. Then kill it. Many times. 

This being said- if you give your word, keep it. It does no harm so long as it does not interfere in a contract, and if it does, well, charge more. If it interferes in the above two rules, then what does it matter, send the bill to the person whose throat you have to clean out from your teeth. 

Cleanliness is important. Bad breath can be smelled. It's hard to ambush people if they can smell you a mile away. Remember that. 

Stat reqs: 

if unclassed: 
10k hp, 5k mana, 5k move 
1 pk of some sort, irregardless of cheap 
roleplay compatable with the Stormcaller ideals 

if classed: 
10k hp + fleshbond/relics, 5k mana, 5k move 
1 status 
roleplay compatable with the Stormcaller ideals 

for ronin: 
5k across and not whining if I don't teach you constantly. You wanted the werewolf before you met my class and clan reqs, so you have to get to the clanning while already classed ones. 
~
