0 Rejuvenation~

Spiritshare - imbue someone with a portion of your strength, taking a measure of their
weakness into yourself

spiritshare <victim>

Strengthen - Give someone hitpoints and move, render them immune to pain

strengthen <victim>

guardianangel - Summon an angelic spirit from the void to defend you for a time.

purify - purify the spirit of a kindred, but be warned, if the vampire is more truly beast
than man, he may fall further towards that savage state.

purify <victim>

empower - Use the power of your aura to cleans and rejuvenate a person, restoring them to
the peak of physical health.

empower <victim>
~

0 ANGEL ANGELS~

These holy beings follow God and the ways of the
righteous. They hunt, and kill, those demons who
wander out of hell, and maybe even those who don't.
Devoted to protecting the sanctity of the lands, they
fight to preserve them against the Wyrm. They often
ally with the followers of Gaia, but foremost in their
mind is the destruction of the Wyrm.

- Each Champion, Angel, or Angel Prince follows a
specific Lord, the Chosen of God.

- Angelic Armour greatly increases an angel's power.
The more, the better.

- Many angels are able to transport themselves to
other angels who follow the same Lord, at will.

- Most angels are able to assume the form of an
angelic weapon.

- The powers of a specific angel vary considerably.
Some are no stronger than the weakest of demons or
vampires, while others are more powerful than the
leaders.

- While in heaven, under the protection of God, an
angel is very difficult to kill indeed.
  
  See 'help Ainparts'
~

0 ANGELARMOUR ANGELARMOR~

Angel armour is the basis of power to each angel.
Though their innate abilities strengthen them greatly,
the armor allows for even greater strength still. Each
color varies considerably.

White is the most basic of angel armor. Gold is the
most advanced, and most expensive. The others follow
in between, from order of White to Gold.
~

0 DEMONARMOR DEMONARMOUR~

Demon armor is the basis of strength for a demon.
Though their innate abilities do strengthen them
greatly, their armor makes them more powerful still.
The strength of each color varies considerably.

Black is the most basic of pieces. Brass, the most
advanced, and most expensive. The others are in
between, in order of strength from black to brass.
~

