0 TAG FREEZETAG REDTALK BLUETALK~

Syntax:
tag <player>
redtalk <message>
bluetalk <message>

Freeze tag is a game with two groups (#R[Red]#n and #L[BLUE]#n)
The object of the game is to freeze ALL members of the opposing
team.

If you tag a member of the opposite team,  they become frozen. And
cannot move until either the game is over,  or they are tagged by
a member of their own color.
~
