0 LEADERBOARD~

List of the best players on the mud, in their respective fields.
Imms are not considered for this list.  The info is writen to a file, so
the data persists through copyovers, and if the person is not online.

Mr. Best PK'er: 
	Calculated by:
ch->pkill * (100 * (ch->pkill * ch->pkill)/((ch->pkill + ch->pdeath) 
	     * (ch->pkill + ch->pdeath)))

Mr. Deadly:		Most player kills.
Mr. Pathetic:		Most player deaths.
Mr. Slayer:		Most mob kills.
Mr. Wimpy:		Most mob deaths
Mr. No life:		Person with most hours.
Mr. Questor:		The quest king. 
~

