0 MAP AUTOMAP~
By enabling long descriptions for rooms (brief must be off),
and enabling the automap feature (type 'map'), then the room
description will include a map of the rooms around the player.

Symbols used for the map are :

#G"#n  Fields
#o¤#n  Hills
#g*#n  Woodland, Forest
#o@#n  Mountain
#nO#n  Inside, City
#L=#n  Water, Ocean, Sea
#C#-#n  Air, Flying
#y+#n  Desert

The symbols '#o|#n' and '#o-#n' represents roads, tunnels, passageways etc.

~
0 MARAUDER~
An offshot of mages known for their bizarre tendancies and lack
of intervention on the part of paradox. Unbound by paradox, random signatures,
no spheres, ie no mgate no ogate and the like. Not recommended for new mages.
~ 
