0 KOE KOTE KINDRED OF THE EAST~
This is a generic help file to spare the staffs ears from
an onslaught of questions. Kindred of the East are in essence,
just as the name states, they are a brand new class for EM
that plays much like a ninja and vampire combined, in short
they are a more melee intensive vampire. They are based almost
exclusively on White Wolf's distinction of so if you would
like more info at this time please visit White-Wolf.com.
Also of note they are not classable or available at this time.
~
